    "content": "<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"600\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120559-1.png\" width=\"812\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>如果要变身野猪，就把原本的野猪编号62254换成拉米姐姐的63008</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"106\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120627-2.png\" width=\"874\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>替换成拉米姐姐的编号</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"109\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120645-3.png\" width=\"881\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>再把怪物列表拉米姐姐的删除</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"96\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120704-4.png\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>把拉米姐姐里的这一段复制到野猪文件里</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"2349\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/2.jpg\" width=\"565\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>上面这段是游戏里变身怪物显示的技能图标</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"360\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120757-5.png\" width=\"458\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>再把拉米姐姐这一段复制到野猪里</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"94\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120812-6.png\" width=\"556\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>还有这一段复制到野猪里</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"771\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120829-8.png\" width=\"850\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>如果怪物文件里没有这个移动的ACT，就要自己增加一个，否则到游戏里是移动不了的</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"92\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120859-9.png\" width=\"390\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>在变身怪物状态下这里，按下对应的键位，它就使用对应的ACT</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"313\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805120909-10.png\" width=\"363\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>再新增一个召回怪物的道具</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"1291\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/6.jpg\" width=\"654\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"518\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805121004-11.png\" width=\"700\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>例如我要变成暴龙王，也是一样的</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"79\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805121026-13.png\" width=\"546\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>换成拉米姐姐的编号63008</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"86\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805121036-14.png\" width=\"565\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"529\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/08/05/image-20230805121102-15.png\" width=\"700\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>还有一种是按Z坐上去的，都是一样的，这样说吧，你想新增变身的，必须要用掉原来变身的编号</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
